OL,3,CKing surprises theatregoers at
OL,4,CShakespeare show in Warwickshire
OL,6,FThe King surprised theatregoers in
OL,7,FWarwickshire when he took a seat to
OL,8,Fwatch a performance of Shakespeare's
OL,9,FThe Tempest play.
OL,11,FCharles was met with cheers from
OL,12,Fcrowds when he arrived at the Royal
OL,13,FShakespeare Theatre in Stratford-upon-
OL,14,FAvon.
OL,16,FHe was greeted by the Lord Lieutenant
OL,17,Fof Warwickshire, Tim Cox, and the
OL,18,FRoyal Shakespeare Company's co-
OL,19,Fartistic directors Daniel Evans and
OL,20,FTamara Harvey.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
