FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779700299
OL,3,CKing surprises theatregoers at
OL,4,CShakespeare show in Warwickshire
OL,6,FAudience members peered down from the
OL,7,Fseating in the dress circle inside the
OL,8,Fauditorium, while others in the stalls
OL,9,Fgot their phones out to take pictures
OL,10,Fwhen Charles took his seat near the
OL,11,Fback between Mr Evans and Ms Harvey.
OL,13,FHe also sat near Sir Richard Eyre, who
OL,14,Fdirected the performance.
OL,16,FMs Harvey said the King was "laughing
OL,17,Faway" next to her during the
OL,18,Fperformance.
OL,20,FShe added: "I think he genuinely
OL,21,Fenjoyed it."
OL,26,@xD@]OUyD@EO]|D@LOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
