FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1779700299
OL,3,CKing surprises theatregoers at
OL,4,CShakespeare show in Warwickshire
OL,6,FMr Evans and Ms Harvey said in a
OL,7,Fstatement: "It was a tremendous honour
OL,8,Fto welcome His Majesty the King back
OL,9,Fto the Royal Shakespeare Theatre for
OL,10,Fthis landmark production of The
OL,11,FTempest, which marks both Sir Kenneth
OL,12,FBranagh's historic return to Stratford-
OL,13,Fupon-Avon for the first time in over
OL,14,F30 years and Sir Richard Eyre's debut
OL,15,Fwith the company after a long and
OL,16,Fdistinguished career directing for the
OL,17,FBritish stage."
OL,26,@oD@LOUyD@OO]
